#

Garlic Herb Tomato Toast

15 min
$3.5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

WheatDairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianQuickHealthy

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

EasySnackAppetizer

Description

A delightful twist on a classic toast, bursting with fresh flavors and a hint of garlic.

Ingredients

  • bread (your choice): 2 slices
  • tomatoes: 1 medium, sliced
  • feta cheese: 1/4 cup, crumbled
  • fresh basil (or herbs of choice): 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • garlic: 1 clove, halved
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
